.DT
short_to_name
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
short_to_name

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
short_to_name -  This function concatenates the short of a group to a valid name that can then be used with create_group().
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string short_to_name(string short)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^short%^RESET%^ - the short of the group
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the name of the group, or "" if invalid

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/group_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This function concatenates the short of a group to a valid name
that can then be used with create_group().  The function will
also return invalid if a channel with such a name exists in the
broadcaster.

.EP

